reviewText: Garbage. Bad shots, editing, action ,acting, Everything. I wonder what the budget was. Probably spent a pretty penny on this crap.

Although I like Werewolf movies this isn't one worth watching. Now if it was set in one location and limit the flash backs for the back stories then got better actors and script then maybe I might've liked it more.
Pure unadulterated garbage. I had no idea what this movie wanted to be but it didn't make it on any level. I made it for 45 minutes and then fell into some kind of coma. Pass!
I'm very happy with this DVD and how the quality came out. Wish they had blu rays but still happy with everything.
A pretty work of art from an independent filmmaker that will surprise you!
